cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.NI, cs.DS, cs.PL

This paper discusses the challenges and developments in auto-scaling web applications in cloud data centers, which involves distributed computing (cs.DC), software engineering (cs.SE), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and programming languages (cs.PL). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.DC, followed by cs.SE, cs.NI, cs.DS, and cs.PL.
